00:16:49.970 --> 00:16:53.770
found by the immune system. So this is first

281
00:16:55.170 --> 00:16:55.770
reason

282
00:16:56.810 --> 00:17:00.090
it's better than ADC. ADC is

283
00:17:02.690 --> 00:17:04.510
positively charged, so it's easy to

284
00:17:05.911 --> 00:17:09.411
attract with the normal cells, is ADC has

285
00:17:09.850 --> 00:17:10.610
more

286
00:17:13.330 --> 00:17:15.050
side effect toxicity.

287
00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:16.891
It's

288
00:17:17.770 --> 00:17:21.590
