00:17:24.590 --> 00:17:27.870
also ADC has shown drug

291
00:17:27.931 --> 00:17:28.630
resistance.

292
00:17:32.330 --> 00:17:33.290
Maybe finally,

293
00:17:34.110 --> 00:17:36.770
what about anti-drug antibodies?

294
00:17:37.530 --> 00:17:37.910
Do you

295
00:17:39.050 --> 00:17:42.930
have any information on how these polysaccharide delivery

