00:31:17.702 --> 00:31:19.222
are short half-life proteins.

522
00:31:21.162 --> 00:31:24.202
Yeah, so the other MYC targets, I think, tend to have longer half-lives.

523
00:31:24.302 --> 00:31:27.942
We haven't looked at any time points shorter than two hours by proteomics.

524
00:31:27.962 --> 00:31:29.062
Okay. Thank you.

