cell activation.

607
00:35:46.862 --> 00:35:50.332
Blocking Cbl-B removes a brake on the immune system,

608
00:35:51.822 --> 00:35:55.742
and Cbl-B deficient mice demonstrate robust T cell

609
00:35:55.782 --> 00:35:59.342
and NK cell mediated tumor immunity, anti-tumor

610
00:35:59.362 --> 00:35:59.862
immunity.

611
00:36:01.762 --> 00:36:05.542
These are some of the data that got us interested, and the field in general,

612
00:36:05.622 --> 00:36:08.722
interested in Cbl as a target for immuno-oncology.

613
00:36:09.582 --> 00:36:13.302
So some time ago in 2011, Paulino and coworkers generated

614
00:36:13.342 --> 00:36:14.722
lines of mice that

615
00:36:14.842 --> 00:36:20.342
have

616
00:36:20.402 --> 00:36:24.042
an inactive Cbl knock in or Cbl, oops, excuse me, or

617
00:36:24.142 --> 00:36:25.172
Cbl knocked out.

618
00:36:26.502 --> 00:36:30.402
And then when T cells were isolated from these mice and stimulated

619
00:36:30.522 --> 00:36:31.162
either with

