690
00:40:45.222 --> 00:40:48.682
and those were filtered by sensogram shape and fit.

691
00:40:48.762 --> 00:40:52.582
We really like SPR for validating hits because it gives you a really nice measure

692
00:40:52.662 --> 00:40:54.882
