723
00:42:48.022 --> 00:42:50.002
which makes it a very nice starting point.

724
00:42:50.382 --> 00:42:54.102
So with all of this information in hand, the medicinal chemistry

725
00:42:54.162 --> 00:42:56.042
team-- Oh, sorry, excuse me. Back up one step.

726
00:42:56.102 --> 00:43:00.078
So what is this molecule actually doing?It binds

727
00:43:00.098 --> 00:43:04.018
to the closed state at the interface of all three of the domains, the

728
00:43:04.058 --> 00:43:07.778
