731
00:43:14.388 --> 00:43:18.188
And so with this, we call this an intramolecular glue inhibitor, and it's

732
00:43:18.418 --> 00:43:21.678
very reminiscent of how the SHP2 inhibitors also work.

733
00:43:25.138 --> 00:43:28.778
So Med Chem team got to work. We were very quickly able

734
00:43:29.118 --> 00:43:32.598
to leverage this structural information provided by

735
00:43:32.658 --> 00:43:36.378
the crystal structure and optimize

736
00:43:36.398 --> 00:43:39.658
