00:44:19.098 --> 00:44:23.038
molecule. And what you can see is that through careful optimization, we were

749
00:44:23.098 --> 00:44:26.538
actually able to increase this significantly as the optimization went along.

750
00:44:29.778 --> 00:44:33.758
So this, NRX-8766, was the first molecule that

751
00:44:33.818 --> 00:44:37.778
