931
00:54:40.138 --> 00:54:44.018
mechanism where they mediated a direct interaction between, in this

932
00:54:44.058 --> 00:54:47.478
case, our target protein ARNT and an E3 ligase,

933
00:54:47.878 --> 00:54:51.418
allowing the target protein to be ubiquitinated and degraded by the proteasome.

934
00:54:52.488 --> 00:54:56.258
And so I'm showing here one representative hit compound, compound A, and we

935
00:54:56.318 --> 00:55:00.258
observed that this compound degraded ARNT in a cellular context in a

936
00:55:00.278 --> 00:55:03.966
dose-dependent manner.And then really importantly, we observed that

